               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-117vb)
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-4vb), incomplete.
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on
                     death (fols. 12rb-16ra)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came
                     from Jerusalem” (fols. 20ra-26vb)
 - Antiphons (kǝśtat, ʾaryām, mazmur)
                     (fols. 33vb-34va, 50rb-51ra, 81va-vb, 83ra-84ra, 88rb-vb, 90ra, 91va-92ra,
                     94va-vb, 98ra-rb)
 - Homily by St Jacob of Sarug for the funeral of priests
                     and deacons (fols. 53vb-55va)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness”
                     (fols. 69ra-71va)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols.
                     71va-73rb)
 - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.
                     77va-79vb)
 - Maṣḥafa ʾardǝʾt “Book of Disciples” (fols. 115va-117vb,
                     1ra-vb)
 
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
